Who Do You Think You Are? US - Season 5, Episode 3




Rachel McAdams

Rachel and her sister Kayleen McAdams discover an English ancestor surrounded by a privileged world, but forced to separate from those he loved; they connect with relatives uprooted by war, and uncover the harrowing circumstances behind their Canadian roots.
